# INSTRUCTIONS: 
# Read & follow the instructions at link below. Edit the two numbers at the top-right below to set the mouse scroll speed.
# Copy this file to ~/.imwheelrc: `cp -i .imwheelrc ~`

# Instructions & help: https://askubuntu.com/questions/254367/permanently-fix-chrome-scroll-speed/991680#991680
# Don't forget:
#   sudo apt update
